---
/** 文风蒸馏：右上操作；配置进弹窗；正文区占满 */
---
<div class="panel novel-workshop-panel novel-style-panel" data-novel-panel="style">
  <div class="novel-panel-head">
    <h2>文风蒸馏</h2>
    <div class="novel-head-actions" aria-label="文风操作">
      <div id="novelStyleSyncBadge" class="novel-sync-badge unsynced">未同步</div>
      <button id="btnStyleCopy" type="button" class="btn btn-fetch novel-btn-sm">复制</button>
      <button id="btnStyleDownload" type="button" class="btn btn-fetch novel-btn-sm">下载</button>
      <button id="btnSyncStyle" type="button" class="btn btn-fetch novel-btn-sm">同步为「文风」</button>
      <button id="btnStyleDistill" type="button" class="btn btn-ai novel-btn-sm">蒸馏文风</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="novel-panel-tip ui-pref-tip">从启用章节抽样分析视角、句式、用词与节奏，产出可复用文风提示词。同步时写入主世界书，条目标题固定为「文风」。</p>
  <p id="novelStyleGate" class="novel-gate-hint" style="display:none;"></p>
  <div id="novelStyleStatus" class="novel-status-text"></div>

  <div class="novel-style-body">
    <div class="novel-style-content">
      <textarea id="novelStyleText" placeholder="文风分析 + 可复用文风提示词会显示在这里，可直接编辑..."></textarea>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="novelModalStyle" class="novel-modal" hidden aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="novel-modal-backdrop" data-novel-modal-close="novelModalStyle"></div>
  <div class="novel-modal-dialog" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="novelModalStyleTitle">
    <div class="novel-modal-head">
      <strong id="novelModalStyleTitle">蒸馏文风</strong>
      <span class="novel-modal-tip">配置抽样与要求后开始 · Esc / 遮罩关闭</span>
    </div>
    <div class="novel-modal-body">
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="novelStyleChunkSize">抽样分片字数（预算上限）</label>
          <select id="novelStyleChunkSize">
            <option value="4000">4,000 字</option>
            <option value="8000">8,000 字</option>
            <option value="12000">12,000 字</option>
            <option value="16000" selected>16,000 字</option>
            <option value="24000">24,000 字</option>
            <option value="32000">32,000 字</option>
            <option value="48000">48,000 字</option>
            <option value="64000">64,000 字</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="novelStyleConflictPolicy">同步冲突策略</label>
          <select id="novelStyleConflictPolicy">
            <option value="merge">合并</option>
            <option value="overwrite">覆盖</option>
            <option value="skip">跳过</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="novelStyleCustom">自定义要求（可选，留空用默认）</label>
        <textarea id="novelStyleCustom" style="min-height:72px;" placeholder="例如：偏冷淡克制，少形容词堆砌"></textarea>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="novel-modal-actions">
      <button type="button" class="btn novel-modal-cancel" data-novel-modal-close="novelModalStyle">取消</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-ai" id="btnStyleDistillConfirm">开始蒸馏</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
